{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"story_flower_set_2_story_1","storyGroup":"story_flower_set_2","storySort":0,"storyDependence":null,"storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":null,"storyName":"树犹如此","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"机缘巧合下，调香师在维多利亚发现了一棵已经在米诺斯绝迹的古树。","storyCanEnter":0,"storyTxt":"obt/memory/story_flower_2_1","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":0,"requiredStages":null,"characters":["莱娜","调香师","帕拉斯","面包店主人","衣着富贵的男人","威廉"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"dialog","id":2},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":5},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","keep":"true","amount":"1","fadetime":"0","id":6},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7a/Avg_bg_bg_courtyard.png","fadetime":"0.5","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$loneliness_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/static/m_avg/m_avg_loneliness_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":8,"musicid":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":9},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":10},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#6$1","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":11},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":12},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱娜","text":"对不起，父亲，母亲。我感染了矿石病。你们的事业当然不会允许一个感染者来继承，现在，我可以做自己想做的事了吧？","id":13,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",5]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱娜","text":"我知道我不能继续留在家里了，我会尽快搬出去，不必为我担心，我已经完全有能力照顾自己了，也不会为家族添麻烦的。","id":14,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#8$1","id":15},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱娜","text":"如果可以的话，能请你们留下我的花园吗？只是一些植物而已，矿石病是不会秽染它们的洁净的。","id":16,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#2$1","id":17},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱娜","text":"请容我告辞了。","id":18,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",1]},{"type":"dialog","id":19},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":20},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":21},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":22},{"type":"character","id":23},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":24},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","keep":"true","amount":"0","fadetime":"0","id":25},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/04/Avg_bg_21_G3_victoria_street_d.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":26},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$m_dia_street_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta3_181101/m_dia_street_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","fadetime":"3","id":27,"musicid":1},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":28},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":29},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","fadetime":"0.5","id":30},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":31},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","focus":"1","id":32},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"冬天。","id":33,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","focus":"2","id":34},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"祭坛中柴火的木屑味。","id":35,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",13]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","focus":"1","id":36},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"遗迹。","id":37,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","focus":"2","id":38},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"神庙里泥土和苔藓的味道。","id":39,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",13]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","focus":"1","id":40},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"夜晚。","id":41,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","focus":"2","id":42},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"赫里亚山林中露水的味道。","id":43,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",13]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","focus":"1","id":44},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"夕阳。","id":45,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","focus":"2","id":46},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"蜂蜜的味道。","id":47,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",13]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#6$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","focus":"1","id":48},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"蜂蜜的味道？","id":49,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#6$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#7","focus":"2","id":50},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"在十二英雄神殿时，每到傍晚，我总习惯于看着夕阳，饮一杯蜂蜜酒。杯中夕阳，和蜂蜜是一般金黄。","id":51,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#6$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#13","focus":"2","id":52},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"唔......那样的景色和味道，都令人十分怀念啊。","id":53,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",12]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#8$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#13","focus":"1","id":54},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"虽然很独特，倒也很容易理解呢。","id":55,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#10$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#13","focus":"1","id":56},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"所以就像这样。只要描述一个情景，我们很容易就能联想到与画面相契合的味道。","id":57,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"反之亦然，当我们闻到某种明显的气味，也会联想到相关的画面。","id":58,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",9]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#10$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#10","focus":"2","id":59},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"所以莱娜小姐认为，用类似的手段可以唤醒葛罗莉亚小姐的回忆？","id":60,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",9]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#10","focus":"1","id":61},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"气味是有唤起感情的能力的，如果气味中的信息足够丰富，脑海中联想的指向性也会更加明确，联系到某一段具体的回忆也是有可能的。","id":62,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"针对葛罗莉亚小姐的病情，这种方式，可能会是一种稳妥的治疗手段。","id":63,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#10","focus":"2","id":64},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"啊，我不会质疑莱娜小姐专业的判断，也并非为这些沉重的植物样本而抱怨，只是有些疑问......","id":65,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"为什么不直接将葛罗莉亚小姐带回这里呢？","id":66,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",9]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#10","focus":"1","id":67},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"呵呵，作为没有战斗能力的医疗干员，远行时是需要有其他人陪同的嘛。这次就麻烦祭司大人啦。","id":68,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"至于为什么不能带葛罗莉亚回来，很可惜，她的身体状况并不允许她长途旅行。另外，将本人带到熟悉的环境也未必会有更好的效果。","id":69,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"就像戏剧里的故事，经过提炼的情节才更容易引起观众情绪的共鸣。过于杂糅的信息，反而会让人难以抓住重点。","id":70,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"就在此时此地，帕拉斯小姐通过闻到的气味，恐怕也很难总结出对这个城市的独特印象吧。","id":71,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#7","focus":"2","id":72},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"的确，寒冷的空气刺激着鼻腔，夹杂着灰尘与油烟的味道。和我所去过的其他现代城市并无差异。","id":73,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",6]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"但是我也注意到，空气里似乎隐隐弥漫着不同寻常的气味，有奶油与小麦的芬芳——这是面包的香味？","id":74,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",6]},{"type":"dialog","id":75},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":76},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#7","focus":"-1","id":77},{"type":"dialogue","name":"面包店主人","text":"哈哈，这位姐姐，请拿两个尝尝吧。不要钱。","id":78,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":79},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":80},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#6","focus":"2","id":81},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"非常感谢您——多么温暖而细腻的味道，我由衷地赞美您的技艺。","id":82,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#6","focus":"-1","id":83},{"type":"dialogue","name":"面包店主人","text":"谢谢夸奖啦，喜欢的话，可以请您帮我多多宣传吗？","id":84,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#6","focus":"2","id":85},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"当然！这样美好的味道当然应该被更多人尝到——莱娜小姐，要尝一个吗？","id":86,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#4$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#6","focus":"1","id":87},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"我还是不用了......帕拉斯小姐，还真是很容易和人打成一片啊。","id":88,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#4$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","focus":"2","id":89},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"与人交谈是一件愉悦的事，可以收获知识，可以磨炼思维。","id":90,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",13]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#6$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","focus":"1","id":91},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"可是这一次任务在于尽快收集必要的素材，如果频繁与别人接触暴露感染者身份的话，又会引起不必要的麻烦。","id":92,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",5]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"如果那个小姑娘知道了我们是感染者，她还会像刚才这样友好吗？","id":93,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#6$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","focus":"2","id":94},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"亲爱的莱娜，与他人接触前，不应预先假设他人的恶意。如先贤所言，“哪怕你见过一百个恶人，也不该断定第一百零一个人会行恶”。","id":95,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",13]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#8$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","focus":"1","id":96},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"如果真是如此的话，我们的生活应该都不是现在这样吧。","id":97,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#8$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#10","focus":"2","id":98},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"莱娜小姐......？","id":99,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",9]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#10$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#10","focus":"1","id":100},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"......没什么，是我过于敏感了。","id":101,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"需要调查、收集的素材有很多，我们得抓紧时间了。","id":102,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",9]},{"type":"dialog","id":103},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.2","fadetime":"2","id":104},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":105},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":106},{"type":"character","id":107},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":108},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/41/Avg_bg_21_G7_decisivebattlealley_d.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":109},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$m_dia_street_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta3_181101/m_dia_street_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","fadetime":"3","id":110,"musicid":2},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":111},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":112},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.4","fadetime":"1","id":113},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","focus":"1","id":114},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"从路边灌木的密度来看，这座城市的气候应该还是偏干燥的。平均年降水量大概在五百毫米左右。","id":115,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"植物生态应该不至于太过复杂。看来工作量比预想的要少一些呢。","id":116,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","focus":"2","id":117},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"这棵树，我似乎在莱娜小姐的温室里也见过，是同一种吗？","id":118,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",13]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#10$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","focus":"1","id":119},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"不一样哦。这棵树是维多利亚柏木，温室里那棵是米诺斯杉树。人们可能会因为鳞叶将二者误认为同一种树。但实际上完全不同呢。","id":120,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",9]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#10$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#6","focus":"2","id":121},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"原来不仅是香料，莱娜小姐对植物的研究也很深啊。","id":122,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#10$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#6","focus":"1","id":123},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"自然界本身就是取之不尽的气味素材库。想要当好一名调香师的话，对于植物的了解也是必不可少的。","id":124,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",9]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#10$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#6","focus":"2","id":125},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"在罗德岛的疗养庭院里，我见过许多来自米诺斯的珍稀植物。其中不少我之前也只在书中见过名字。","id":126,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",5]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"想来莱娜小姐，也一定深深眷恋着米诺斯的一草一木吧。","id":127,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#10$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#6","focus":"1","id":128},{"type":"multiline","name":"调香师","text":"不管在哪里，植物总是可爱的呀——","id":129},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#6$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#6","focus":"1","id":130},{"type":"multiline","name":"调香师","text":"奇怪，为什么在这种气候下，还能见到这么多树蕨？是有人专门照料吗......","id":131},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#6$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#6","focus":"2","id":132},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"其实，莱娜小姐方才说的一句话，还是令我颇为在意。","id":133,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",5]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"莱娜小姐，也是因为矿石病离开故乡的吗？","id":134,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#6","focus":"1","id":135},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"它的香气并不突出，但就像空气味道的一种底色，需要采样记录呢。帕拉斯小姐，可以取一支三号试管给我吗——抱歉，您刚才说什么？","id":136,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","focus":"2","id":137},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"三号试管，是这个吗？","id":138,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",13]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","focus":"1","id":139},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"不对，是右边那个大一号的。对，谢谢。","id":140,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#8$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","focus":"1","id":141},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"唔，离开家乡的原因......很复杂呢。","id":142,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"时间过去太久，当时的心情都已经模糊了，只记得许多遗憾和失落堆积起来，最后只剩下“我一定要离开”这样的想法。","id":143,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#8$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#13","focus":"2","id":144},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"每一个游子都有着无奈，在这方面，我们一定都有许多难以对外人言说的愁绪可以分享。","id":145,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",12]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#13","focus":"1","id":146},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"帕拉斯小姐言重啦。都已经是陈年往事了。我现在也找到了自己的归属和事业，没什么好遗憾的。","id":147,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#13","focus":"2","id":148},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"我亲爱的同乡，虽然拖着这副病躯远离故土，时至今日，我也能感受到米诺斯每一处草树、每一块山岩的呼唤。","id":149,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",12]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"我衷心期盼着，或许有朝一日，我们都能回到故乡——","id":150,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",12]},{"type":"dialog","id":151},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":152},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#6$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#13","focus":"1","id":153},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":154},{"type":"playsound","key":"$bottlebroken","volume":"1","id":155},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":156},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"抱歉......我太不小心了。","id":157,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#6$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#1","focus":"2","id":158},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"莱娜——","id":159,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#8$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#1","focus":"1","id":160},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"......帕拉斯小姐，可以请您停止这个话题吗？","id":161,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#8$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#10","focus":"2","id":162},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"莱娜？","id":163,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",9]},{"type":"dialog","id":164},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":165},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$drift_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_drift_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":166,"musicid":3},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#6$1","id":167},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"明明没有做错什么，只是因为一场意外，就被剥夺了所有身份，所有价值。以帕拉斯小姐的经历，应该是可以理解的吧？","id":168,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",5]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"难道您认为，这些都是不必记恨、无需挂怀的小事吗？","id":169,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_482_pallas_1#3","id":170},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"无可否认的是，这片大地对感染者是格外残酷的，我也曾质问过这不公正的命运，可最终，信念与希望还是胜过了怨恨。","id":171,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",2]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"莱娜，我当然无权告诉你不该记恨什么，只是对于养育我们的故土，或者是身边的亲人朋友——是否还有任何一分怀恋呢？","id":172,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#6$1","id":173},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"诚如您所言。但将我逐出故乡的，不是矿石病，正是将我当作再无价值的工具而抛弃的家人，是冷眼旁观、幸灾乐祸的朋友。","id":174,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",5]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"直到今天，米诺斯也还在传唱着那些浪漫的诗篇、英雄的故事。你我的遭遇，所有感染者的遭遇，都只能算作故事里碍眼的瑕疵吧。","id":175,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",5]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"帕拉斯小姐，对您来说，米诺斯是一个值得怀念的地方。那里有您的梦想和信仰。但是于我而言，这只是一个我现在不想回想起的名字。","id":176,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",5]},{"type":"dialog","id":177},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":178},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#2$1","id":179},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"......对不起，我失态了。","id":180,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_482_pallas_1#4","id":181},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"不，我应该道歉。唤起了你不好的回忆，我感到万分抱歉。","id":182,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","id":183},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"没什么。比起沉浸在不愉快的回忆里，现在还有更重要的事情要做吧。","id":184,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","id":185},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"说得对，我们正需要在当下找到一些意义，来冲淡往日的愁绪......","id":186,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",13]},{"type":"dialog","id":187},{"type":"character","name":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","focus":"-1","id":188},{"type":"playsound","key":"$leaveshake","volume":"1","id":189},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":190},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#6$1","id":191},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"......得利斯木？","id":192,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_482_pallas_1#10","id":193},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"一种已经绝迹的树吗？它对莱娜小姐有何特殊意义呢？","id":194,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",9]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#6$1","id":195},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"为什么，这里会有一棵得利斯木？","id":196,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",5]},{"type":"dialog","id":197},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":198},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":199},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":200},{"type":"character","id":201},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":202},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/70/Avg_bg_bg_forest.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":203},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$m_dia_street_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta3_181101/m_dia_street_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":204,"musicid":4},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":205},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":206},{"type":"text","text":"一片杂草丛生的山坡上，立着一棵突兀的古树。","id":207},{"type":"text","text":"树干还算笔直，但并不粗壮。粗糙的树皮显得饱经风霜。稀疏的树冠似破碎的伞骨，只剩零星几片树叶挂在枝头。","id":208},{"type":"character","name":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","id":209},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"得利斯木。生长于米诺斯，也仅仅生长在米诺斯。以坚硬无比的木质闻名，在诸多诗歌与戏剧中，都是坚强不屈的代名词。","id":210,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",13]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"在萨尔贡入侵时期，侵略者为了摧毁我们的信仰，对我们的文化大肆破坏，这种树也是其中的牺牲品。","id":211,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",13]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"我们英勇的战士击退了侵略者后，也再没有人在米诺斯境内见过这种树。","id":212,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",13]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"如若不是典籍中的记载，人们几乎要以为它是传说中的植物。莱娜小姐又怎么能确认眼前这棵树就是得利斯木呢？","id":213,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",13]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","id":214},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"帕拉斯小姐......能否借用一下您的武器？","id":215,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":216},{"type":"character","id":217},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":218},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"40","ystrength":"40","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":219},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_axeimp","volume":"1","id":220},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":221},{"type":"playsound","key":"$leaveshake","volume":"1","id":222},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#8$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","focus":"2","id":223},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"“刀剑斧钺，斫之无痕。”书上是这么记载的。但这样轻轻一砍，就能砍断树枝。","id":224,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",13]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"而且书中描绘的得利斯木，的确不像是这般瘦弱的样子......","id":225,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",13]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#8$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","focus":"1","id":226},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"同一种植物生长在不同环境，呈现的性状也会有极大的差异。但就像人的样貌相差甚远，我们也不会将一个黎博利误认成萨弗拉。","id":227,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"树叶锯齿一般的轮廓，边缘红色的纹路，还有极短的叶柄，这些特征都和古籍中记载的一模一样。","id":228,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"虽然因为不同的环境，木质变得疏松脆弱，但依然保留着细腻规整的纹理，树皮内还残存的油性树脂......不会错的。","id":229,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","focus":"1","id":230},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"最重要的是，这棵树，有米诺斯的味道。","id":231,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","focus":"-1","id":232},{"type":"text","text":"有风吹过，周遭草木一片肃杀。","id":233},{"type":"text","text":"羸弱的古树迎风颔首，似乎是对远道而来的同乡致意。","id":234},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","focus":"2","id":235},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"传闻得利斯木灭绝已久，这棵树看起来也有数十年的岁月。可它究竟，是如何来到这异国他乡的呢？","id":236,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",13]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#10$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","focus":"1","id":237},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"或许是羽兽衔走果实，或许是风吹走种子。自然有时会给生命奇妙的生机，但更多时候，还是会无情地夺走生命。","id":238,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"帕拉斯小姐，我想，救下这棵树。","id":239,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",9]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#10$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#1","focus":"2","id":240},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"可现在不是树木结种的时期，将这棵树连根移走更不可能。这种情况下......","id":241,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",0]},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"8","id":242},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#10$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#1","focus":"1","id":243},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"我或许有个主意......虽然不太愿意做这种事，但是也没有选择了。","id":244,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"帕拉斯小姐，您在米诺斯的时候，演过戏剧吗？","id":245,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",9]},{"type":"dialog","id":246},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":247},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":248},{"type":"stopmusic","id":249},{"type":"character","id":250},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":251},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/70/Avg_bg_bg_forest.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":252},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$path_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/a001/m_dia_path_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","fadetime":"2","id":253,"musicid":5},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":254},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":255},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_177","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":256},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":257},{"type":"dialogue","name":"衣着富贵的男人","text":"呼，呼......这个路，怎么这么难走，真不知道负责城建的官员到底在干什么......莱娜小姐，怎么会约我在这种地方见面？","id":258,"figure":"avg_npc_177"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#10$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#1","focus":"1","id":259},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"威廉先生，好久不见。真是不好意思，感染者不方便在城里抛头露面，只能烦劳您跑一趟啦。","id":260,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",9]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_177","id":261},{"type":"dialogue","name":"威廉","text":"太遗憾了，这世上太多愚人被偏见蒙蔽双眼——不，我也没有冒犯令尊的意思，不久前我才拜访过他，他老人家身体还很硬朗。","id":262,"figure":"avg_npc_177"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"威廉","text":"但作为您的知己，我是十分清楚的，莱娜小姐的价格——不，莱娜小姐对于香水界的价值，又怎该因矿石病而蒙尘呢？","id":263,"figure":"avg_npc_177"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"威廉","text":"在莱娜小姐的指导下，我们公司的香水，一推出就占据了维多利亚各大市场，全年销售额达到了三百万维镑！简直堪称艺术品！","id":264,"figure":"avg_npc_177"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#3$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#1","focus":"1","id":265},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"（说得倒好听，明明就是偷我的配方。要是我没有离家，你还敢这么做吗？）","id":266,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",2]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"（而且，居然才三百万吗？）","id":267,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#1","focus":"1","id":268},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"咳，我来介绍一下，这位是威廉先生，我的......朋友，是维多利亚著名的香水艺术家。","id":269,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"这位则是我的同乡，帕拉斯，也是您的同行。","id":270,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":271},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","focus":"2","id":272},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"威廉先生，久闻大名。我即使是在米诺斯也有所耳闻，今日一见，果然......果然，很像一名香水艺术家！","id":273,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",13]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_177","id":274},{"type":"dialogue","name":"威廉","text":"幸会幸会，既然是同行，莱娜小姐今日引见，一定是有生意吧？","id":275,"figure":"avg_npc_177"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","focus":"1","id":276},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"的确是生意的事，但其实是希望您看在我们过去的交情上，帮我们一个忙。","id":277,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_177","id":278},{"type":"dialogue","name":"威廉","text":"帮忙？这......","id":279,"figure":"avg_npc_177"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","focus":"2","id":280},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"这款香水是在下拙作。并非在下自夸，它在米诺斯也算家喻户晓的商品。在下也有以它为核心打造香水品牌的计划。","id":281,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",13]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"威廉先生，你我都是以生产香气为业，以贩卖香气为生。我们的追求，也一定不仅限于金钱，而是希望将香气与幸福，传递到大地各处——","id":282,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",13]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_177","id":283},{"type":"dialogue","name":"威廉","text":"哈哈......您说的很有道理，所以——您到底想说什么？","id":284,"figure":"avg_npc_177"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","focus":"1","id":285},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"咳咳，帕拉斯小姐，威廉先生是我的朋友，不妨就把你的困难直接告诉他吧。","id":286,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","id":287},{"type":"dialog","id":288},{"type":"move","name":"left","xpos":"50","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":289},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":290},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","focus":"1","id":291},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"（说重点，重点！）","id":292,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":293},{"type":"move","name":"left","xpos":"-50","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":294},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":295},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#6","focus":"2","id":296},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"当然，当然。对于朋友，我应该坦诚相待。","id":297,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",5]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"威廉先生，我想将自己的作品带入维多利亚市场。这款香水，其他材料还好说，但作为最重要原料的一种树木，原先只能在米诺斯找到。","id":298,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",5]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"或许是天意如此，我在这座城市里居然也找到了这种树木。请看。","id":299,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_177","id":300},{"type":"dialogue","name":"威廉","text":"您说的主要原料，就是这片树叶？","id":301,"figure":"avg_npc_177"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"威廉","text":"的确有种特殊的香气，运用在香水中，使整体显得沉稳古典。与市面上多数木质调香水都不一样。","id":302,"figure":"avg_npc_177"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#6","focus":"2","id":303},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"这是米诺斯香柏。既然在这座城市发现了它的生长痕迹，就证明它也能适应这里的气候。","id":304,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",5]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"所以，我想在这座城市承包一块土地来大量种植。但作为异国商人，手续上有诸多不便。所以希望您在这方面，能施以援手。","id":305,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_177","id":306},{"type":"dialogue","name":"威廉","text":"可是这件事，凭我的关系，也只怕不容易啊。","id":307,"figure":"avg_npc_177"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#6","focus":"2","id":308},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"威廉先生，既然是谈生意，我们不如开门见山。您不用担心这个品牌会抢占市场。只要您愿意给予一些帮助，我们当然也会回馈利润。","id":309,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",5]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"您看这样如何？在商品进入市场一年内，我们会完全依赖您的销售渠道。","id":310,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_177","id":311},{"type":"dialogue","name":"威廉","text":"哈哈哈......怎么会呢。以我和莱娜小姐的交情，就算没有任何好处，我肯定也该关照一些。","id":312,"figure":"avg_npc_177"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"威廉","text":"我只是有些好奇，莱娜小姐也认为这款香水有支撑起一个品牌的潜力？","id":313,"figure":"avg_npc_177"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#10$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#6","focus":"1","id":314},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"这我可不敢妄言。在市场方面，您才是行家。作为调香师，我只能就作品本身给出一些评价。","id":315,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"近年木质调香水颇受欢迎，“异域风情”也是容易引起话题的词语。这款香水自身品质也不俗。综合考虑，您应该有自己的判断才是。","id":316,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",9]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_177","id":317},{"type":"dialogue","name":"威廉","text":"嗯，您说的很有道理。另外还想问问，您说的这种树，具体是在哪里找到的？","id":318,"figure":"avg_npc_177"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#10$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#1","focus":"2","id":319},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"这说来也巧，就在这片山坡上，离此处——","id":320,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#10$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#1","focus":"1","id":321},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"咳咳，帕拉斯小姐，就算是合作对象，有些事情也不该现在说哦。","id":322,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",9]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_177","id":323},{"type":"dialogue","name":"威廉","text":"哈，哈哈，说的是啊。容我想想，想想......","id":324,"figure":"avg_npc_177"},{"type":"dialog","id":325},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_cloakmovement","volume":"1","id":326},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":327},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#3$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#1","focus":"1","id":328},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"（啊，若无其事地就把样品和树叶装进口袋了。）","id":329,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_177","id":330},{"type":"dialogue","name":"威廉","text":"哎。承包土地的事，说好办也好办，说麻烦也麻烦。给我几天时间，二位少安毋躁，等我的消息吧。","id":331,"figure":"avg_npc_177"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"威廉","text":"在我回复之前，千万不要擅自行动啊。我就先告辞了，告辞......","id":332,"figure":"avg_npc_177"},{"type":"dialog","id":333},{"type":"character","fadetime":"1","id":334},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":335},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":336},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","focus":"2","id":337},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"唔，演戏实在不是我所长......我刚刚有说错台词吗？","id":338,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",13]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","focus":"1","id":339},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"一句都没有说对哦。","id":340,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#8","focus":"2","id":341},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"呜......","id":342,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#10$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#8","focus":"1","id":343},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"开玩笑啦。虽然和剧本有些出入，不过一个人满眼都是利益的时候，就很难注意到别的东西了。","id":344,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"做得不错，帕拉斯小姐。我们的目的应该已经达到了。","id":345,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",9]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#10$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","focus":"2","id":346},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"商场中的阴谋，比战场上的兵法更加难以捉摸......接下来我们该怎么办？","id":347,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",13]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#10$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","focus":"1","id":348},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"该怎么办呢，不如就如我们的这位朋友所说，先回去休息，安心等待吧。","id":349,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",9]},{"type":"dialog","id":350},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":351},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":352},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":353},{"type":"character","id":354},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":355},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","keep":"true","amount":"1","fadetime":"0","id":356},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/5d/Avg_bg_bg_falls_1.png","fadetime":"0.5","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":357},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$newhope01_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta3_181101/m_dia_newhope01_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","fadetime":"2","id":358,"musicid":6},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":359},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":360},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#8$1","id":361},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱娜","text":"终于找到了。","id":362,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱娜","text":"金葵花，通常生长在水边。其中重瓣的花一直被当作特殊品种，实际上应该是另一个种类呢。","id":363,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱娜","text":"虽然长相和生长环境都十分相似，但幼苗的形态是截然不同的。仔细闻闻的话，香味也有很大区别呢。","id":364,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","id":365},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱娜","text":"还是给你起一个自己的名字吧，我想想，就叫落日葵怎么样？","id":366,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":367},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.2","fadetime":"2","id":368},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":369},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":370},{"type":"character","id":371},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":372},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ec/Avg_bg_bg_jungle_1.png","fadetime":"0.5","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":373},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.4","fadetime":"2","id":374},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":375},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":376},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","id":377},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱娜","text":"“硬叶桐的树叶有治疗伤口的效果”，书中是这么写的。其实并不准确。","id":378,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱娜","text":"实际上，是树叶中的酸性液体可以杀灭病菌，但这也和土壤条件有关，简单地将它视作药用植物实在是太草率了。","id":379,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#3$1","id":380},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱娜","text":"书上的错误还有很多，把这些错误挑出来的话，都够编写另一本书了呢。有时间的话，不如自己来写一本吧。","id":381,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",2]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱娜","text":"如果有时间的话......","id":382,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",2]},{"type":"dialog","id":383},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.2","fadetime":"2","id":384},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":385},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":386},{"type":"character","id":387},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":388},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d2/Avg_bg_bg_desert_3.png","fadetime":"0.5","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":389},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.4","fadetime":"2","id":390},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":391},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":392},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","id":393},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱娜","text":"荒野上的红芒草和花店里的赤月兰，任谁都不会想到它们原先是同一种植物吧。","id":394,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱娜","text":"为了适应干旱的环境，红芒草的叶片变成了这种细小的样子，不过二者的种子，依然保留着同样的形态。","id":395,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",0]},{"type":"multiline","name":"莱娜","text":"这也证明了，或许在数百年前，这片荒野也是另一种景象。如果这个发现可——","id":396},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"20","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":397},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#2$1","id":398},{"type":"multiline","name":"莱娜","text":"咳，咳咳咳......","id":399},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#9$1","id":400},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱娜","text":"......最近体力下降了很多啊。","id":401,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",8]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱娜","text":"加油啊莱娜，现在还没到感叹力不从心的时候！红芒草还在这顽强地活着，你也可以......","id":402,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",8]},{"type":"dialog","id":403},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":404},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":405},{"type":"character","id":406},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":407},{"type":"subtitle","text":"如果，我也只是一株无名芒草。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"23","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":408},{"type":"subtitle","text":"是不是也可以无忧无虑地在这里扎根生长了呢？","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"23","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":409},{"type":"subtitle","id":410},{"type":"dialog","id":411},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":412},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","keep":"true","amount":"0","fadetime":"0","id":413},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_bg_bg_black.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":414},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":415},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":416},{"type":"text","text":"三日后","id":417},{"type":"dialog","id":418},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":419},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/70/Avg_bg_bg_forest.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":420},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":421},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":422},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":423},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":424},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$warm_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_warm_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","fadetime":"2","id":425,"musicid":7},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","fadetime":"0.5","id":426},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":427},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","focus":"2","id":428},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"我记得，就是这附近。","id":429,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",13]},{"type":"dialog","id":430},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":431},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","focus":"1","id":432},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"看那边。","id":433,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":434},{"type":"character","id":435},{"type":"text","text":"远远望去，山坡上的古树一如几日前的憔悴模样，但被许多全副武装的人层层把守着。","id":436},{"type":"text","text":"附近的一大片空地也被篱笆围起，立着一块显眼的告示牌。","id":437},{"type":"dialog","id":438},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","fadetime":"0.5","id":439},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":440},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","focus":"2","id":441},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"“私人领地，非请勿入”？","id":442,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",13]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#14","focus":"1","id":443},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"虽说是无利不起早，但威廉先生的执行力还是远远超过了我的想象啊。嗯，值得表扬。","id":444,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#1","focus":"2","id":445},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"仅靠一片树叶就在这片偌大的树林里找到那一株树木，也算是精神可嘉了。","id":446,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#3$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#1","focus":"1","id":447},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"就算我们开出了那样的条件他还不满足，还是想要把这个香水完全占为己有呢。不过很可惜，这次他怕是不能如愿了。","id":448,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",2]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"那份香水样本里，并没有用到得利斯木。只是我用几种植物模拟出的味道骗过了他的鼻子。他继续研究下去，只会钻进死胡同吧。","id":449,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#3$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#10","focus":"2","id":450},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"莱娜早就已经预料到了这一步吗？","id":451,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",9]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#10$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#10","focus":"1","id":452},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"小时候，在家里也算是耳濡目染。虽然很讨厌，但那一套话术和所谓的“商业思维”，再熟悉不过啦。","id":453,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"总之，这下应该不用担心了。不出意外的话，等来年开春，这片山坡就会种满得利斯木的幼苗了吧。","id":454,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"小小地欺骗了他一下，虽说也可以当作对他之前抄袭我的配方的惩罚，但心里还是有些过意不去呢。","id":455,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"还是等有空的时候，真的以得利斯木为原料设计一份配方送给他吧。","id":456,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",9]},{"type":"dialog","id":457},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":458},{"type":"character","name":"avg_482_pallas_1#5","id":459},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"莱娜小姐，其实我有一个疑问。","id":460,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"如果真如你所说，米诺斯给你留下的，只有失望与怨恨的话，你又为何要在意这一棵树的命运呢？","id":461,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",4]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#8$1","id":462},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"草木无言，只是深深扎根于这片土地。又有哪株植物，可以真正离开养育它的土壤而活呢？","id":463,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","id":464},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"另外，帕拉斯小姐说的不对哦。","id":465,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"虽然在故乡有过种种不好的回忆，时至今日我也不能与过去和解。但我又怎能说，在憎恨那片土地呢？","id":466,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"我的理想至今都没有改变过，我想要为这片土地保留下美好的事物。也许在遥远的将来，还有人因为我的工作能感受到它们的芬芳。","id":467,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":468},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.2","fadetime":"1","id":469},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":470},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":471},{"type":"character","id":472},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":473},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":474},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.4","fadetime":"1","id":475},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":476},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#1","focus":"2","id":477},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"莱娜，到返回罗德岛的时间了。","id":478,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#1","focus":"1","id":479},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"嗯，要带回去的样本已经收拾好了。就要麻烦帕拉斯大人帮忙一起搬回去啦。","id":480,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#1","focus":"2","id":481},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"当然，乐意效劳。是房间门口那一小包吗？","id":482,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#1","focus":"1","id":483},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"是旅馆楼下的那一大箱哦。","id":484,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":485},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"avg_482_pallas_1#1","focus":"2","id":486},{"type":"dialogue","name":"帕拉斯","text":"好......好吧，作为祭司，服务于米诺斯的人民，也是理所应当的......","id":487,"figure":["avg_482_pallas_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":488},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":489},{"type":"move","name":"right","xpos":"300","fadetime":"2","block":"false","id":490},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","name2":"char_empty","fadetime":"0.5","id":491},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":492},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#8$1","id":493},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"是啊。你也是跨越了千山万水，落在一个陌生的地方，有了不一样的名字，不一样的身份，不一样的价值。","id":494,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"故乡的风雪或许凛冽，但离开了熟悉的暖阳与甘霖，又怎能安心扎根呢？","id":495,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"是米诺斯孕育了你，而你也将重塑米诺斯的模样。","id":496,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_181_flower_1#1$1","id":497},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"先再见啦。","id":498,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"调香师","text":"总有一天，我会和你一起回到故乡。","id":499,"figure":["avg_181_flower_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":500},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":501},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":502},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":503},{"type":"character","id":504},{"type":"image","id":505}],"characters":["莱娜","调香师","帕拉斯","面包店主人","衣着富贵的男人","威廉"]}